== Kakooza Nkuliza Charles ==
Kakooza wamamaye kwizina rya KNC izina rimaze kumenyekana cyane mu [[Rwanda]] ndetse no [[Akarere ka Muhanga|mu karere]] kubera ibikorwa bye<ref>https://igihe.com/abantu/article/urugendo-rutangaje-rwa-knc-watangije-radio-acengana-na-leta</ref>

KNC yamamaye [[UMUZIKI|nkumunyamuziki]] umukinnyi wikinamico ndetse nkumunyamakuru wikorera ufite radio na television ye bwite

bizwi nka Radio 1 na TV1 bikorera i [[Kigali]] mu [[Umurenge wa Kacyiru|murenge wa Kacyiru]] akagira kandi ikipe yumupira w'amaguru izwi nka Gasogi fc<ref>https://bwiza.com/?Impaka-kuri-Sophia-n-ibyapa-Rwabuze-gica-hagati-ya-CP-Kabera-na-KNC</ref>

== Ibikorwa ==
KNC ni umuyobozi wa [[Radio Studio 54 Network|Radio 1 na TV1]] ndtetse ni ibye kugiticye akaba umunyamuziki [[Filimi ya Seburikoko|umukinnyi wa film nikinamico]]<ref>https://ibyamamare.com/knc-yatunguwe-nakayabo-ka-miliyoni-99-kwizera-olivier-arikwishyuza-gasogi-united-yakiniraga/</ref>

akaba umunyamakuru umwanditsi umuyobozi wibitaramo ndetse akaba umuhanga mu kwamamaza ibikorwa byabashoramari

nibindi akaba afite ikipe izwi nka Gasogi FC iri mukiciro cyambere mu [[Rwanda]]<ref>https://rwandaexpress.blogspot.com/2012/03/rwanda-knc-ni-muntu-ki.html</ref>

== Agasha ==
KNC ubwo yigaga mu i[[Ishuri|shuri]] rizwi nka [[Lycée de Kigali|Lycee de Kigali]] yashinze ihuriro ryabahanzi nabaririmbyi yise  the Earth Light ryarimo

bamwe mubyamamare bizwi cyane mu Rwanda nka [[UMUZIKI|Tom close]] Manasseh Mico ndetse nabandi benshi batandukanye

icyogihe basubiragamo [[Indirimbo y’igihugu|indirimbo]] zabandi bagategura i[[UMUZIKI|bitaramo]] kwinjira byari inote yijana 100 yashoboraga gutegura 

igitaramo akuzuza inzu yimyidagaduro ya l[[Lycée de Kigali|ycee de Kigali]]<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/ubutabera/imanza/KNC-yagizwe-umwere-mu-rubanza-yarezwemo-n-uwo-bashinganye-Radio-One</ref>

